291704e5c6b976776d6d870d1c0a9e016154f6512cf24334a39ecb32f103e8f5fb683d9772199dc875eb79b769b3b036d150e02ac056bb08bdb4850c475660aa  skip-test-memset_explicit-on-arm.patch
"
